{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775896197099,"sessionID":"ses_28458e356ffeChgVTor3S6GXRb","part":{"id":"prt_d7ba977ca001MPt3z0xDmBUD0W","messageID":"msg_d7ba84a6c001dsXH63ptV1LxPh","sessionID":"ses_28458e356ffeChgVTor3S6GXRb","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-d7d1e467ba9e4c8197be4181a8140d50","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/workloadmanager/tasks.md","content":"# AR-038: Go Unit Tests for pkg/workloadmanager\n\n## Overview\n- **Module**: pkg/workloadmanager\n- **Language**: Go\n- **Size**: L\n- **Design**: Stage ST-3 completed\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### Phase 1: Core Package Tests (Enhancement)\n\n#### 1.1 Store Tests - Concurrent Operations\n- [ ] Add stress test for concurrent read/write operations (1000+ operations)\n- [ ] Add test for concurrent ListExpiredSandboxes with ongoing deletes\n- [ ] Add test for concurrent ListInactiveSandboxes with ongoing updates\n- [ ] Add edge case test: limit=0 behavior in ListExpired/ListInactive\n\n#### 1.2 Types Tests - Error Handling Edge Cases\n- [ ] Add test for ConflictError.Error() method\n- [ ] Add test for HandleError with ConflictError type\n- [ ] Add test for HandleError JSON encoding failure scenario\n- [ ] Add test for ErrorResponse/SuccessResponse JSON marshaling\n\n#### 1.3 Lifecycle Tests - Error Scenarios\n- [ ] Add test for DeleteSandbox with K8s API conflict error\n- [ ] Add test for DeleteSandbox with K8s API internal error\n- [ ] Add test for ForceDeleteSandbox with SandboxClaimKind\n- [ ] Add test for DeleteSandbox context timeout behavior\n- [ ] Add test for ForceDeleteSandbox context timeout behavior\n- [ ] Add test for UpdateSandboxStatus with NotFound error\n\n---\n\n### Phase 2: Server & Router Tests (Enhancement)\n\n#### 2.1 HTTPServer Tests\n- [ ] Add test for NewHTTPServerWithClients constructor\n- [ ] Add test for HTTPServer with garbage collector Start/Stop\n- [ ] Add test for server timeout configuration propagation\n- [ ] Add test for RegisterHandler multiple handlers\n- [ ] Add test for Stop with already stopped server\n- [ ] Add test for Start when already running (error handling)\n\n#### 2.2 Router Tests\n- [ ] Add test for RegisterHandlers with empty list\n- [ ] Add test for Router with middleware chain\n- [ ] Add test for Router method not allowed handling\n- [ ] Add test for Router path pattern matching\n\n---\n\n### Phase 3: K8s Client & Informers Tests (Enhancement)\n\n#### 3.1 K8sClient Tests\n- [ ] Add test for ClientCache concurrent GetOrCreateClient\n- [ ] Add test for ClientCache with invalid rest.Config\n- [ ] Add test for K8sClient.SetClients method\n- [ ] Add test for WaitForCacheSync with partial sync failure\n- [ ] Add test for DynamicClient/CoreClient nil handling\n\n#### 3.2 Informers Tests\n- [ ] Add test for Informers with multiple namespace filtering\n- [ ] Add test for WaitForCacheSync returning false scenario\n- [ ] Add test for Informers Start with cancelled context\n- [ ] Add test for NewInformers with nil k8sClient\n\n---\n\n### Phase 4: Garbage Collector Tests (Enhancement)\n\n#### 4.1 GC Core Tests\n- [ ] Add test for runOnce with empty store\n- [ ] Add test for runOnce with all sandboxes expired (batch > total)\n- [ ] Add test for runOnce with mixed expired/inactive order\n- [ ] Add test for SetIdleTimeout during active GC run\n- [ ] Add test for GetStats immutability (snapshot)\n- [ ] Add test for GC interval zero handling (default fallback)\n\n#### 4.2 GC Error Handling Tests\n- [ ] Add test for runOnce when store.ListExpiredSandboxes returns error\n- [ ] Add test for runOnce when store.ListInactiveSandboxes returns error\n- [ ] Add test for runOnce when DeleteSandbox returns InternalError\n- [ ] Add test for runOnce when DeleteSandbox returns ConflictError\n\n---\n\n### Phase 5: Handlers Tests (Enhancement)\n\n#### 5.1 Health Handler Tests\n- [ ] Add test for HealthChecker.IsHealthy() integration\n- [ ] Add test for concurrent /healthz requests\n- [ ] Add test for concurrent /readyz requests\n- [ ] Add test for healthz/readyz with query parameters\n\n#### 5.2 Deletion Handler Tests\n- [ ] Add test for handleDeleteError with ServiceUnavailableError\n- [ ] Add test for handleDeleteError with ConflictError\n- [ ] Add test for handleDeleteError with unknown error type\n- [ ] Add test for deletion with force flag (future feature prep)\n- [ ] Add test for deletion with custom grace period\n- [ ] Add test for concurrent deletion requests same session\n\n#### 5.3 Handler Adapter Tests\n- [ ] Add test for HandlerFunc with multiple error types\n- [ ] Add test for HandlerFuncAdapter with invalid path\n- [ ] Add test for HandlerFunc concurrent requests\n\n---\n\n### Phase 6: Middleware Tests (Enhancement)\n\n#### 6.1 CORS Middleware Tests\n- [ ] Add test for multiple origins in same request\n- [ ] Add test for allowed headers comma-separated values\n- [ ] Add test for OPTIONS preflight with credentials\n- [ ] Add test for CORS with no allowed origins configured\n\n#### 6.2 Logging Middleware Tests\n- [ ] Add test for logging with response body write\n- [ ] Add test for logging captures query parameters\n- [ ] Add test for logging captures request headers\n- [ ] Add test for logging duration accuracy (millisecond precision)\n- [ ] Add test for concurrent request logging (no interleaving)\n\n#### 6.3 Recovery Middleware Tests\n- [ ] Add test for panic with different types (string, error, struct)\n- [ ] Add test for nested panic recovery\n- [ ] Add test for recovery preserving other middleware state\n- [ ] Add test for recovery with custom error message\n\n---\n\n### Phase 7: Integration Tests (Enhancement)\n\n#### 7.1 E2E Scenario Tests\n- [ ] Add test for full request lifecycle: create -> delete\n- [ ] Add test for server restart scenario\n- [ ] Add test for graceful shutdown with pending requests\n- [ ] Add test for health check during GC run\n- [ ] Add test for multiple handlers registered on same server\n\n#### 7.2 Edge Case Integration Tests\n- [ ] Add test for server with zero timeout config\n- [ ] Add test for server with negative timeout (error handling)\n- [ ] Add test for middleware chain with panic in first middleware\n- [ ] Add test for large request body handling\n\n---\n\n### Phase 8: Coverage Verification\n\n#### 8.1 Coverage Analysis\n- [ ] Run go test -coverprofile=coverage.out ./pkg/workloadmanager/...\n- [ ] Identify functions/methods with <80% coverage\n- [ ] Generate coverage report for each sub-package\n- [ ] Document coverage gaps in coverage-gaps.md\n\n#### 8.2 Coverage Target Achievement\n- [ ] Ensure pkg/workloadmanager coverage >= 80%\n- [ ] Ensure pkg/workloadmanager/handlers coverage >= 80%\n- [ ] Ensure pkg/workloadmanager/middleware coverage >= 80%\n- [ ] Add missing tests for uncovered code paths\n\n---\n\n## Verification Commands\n\n```bash\n# Run all tests\ngo test ./pkg/workloadmanager/... -v\n\n# Run with coverage\ngo test ./pkg/workloadmanager/... -coverprofile=coverage.out -covermode=atomic\n\n# View coverage by function\ngo tool cover -func=coverage.out\n\n# Generate HTML coverage report\ngo tool cover -html=coverage.out -o coverage.html\n\n# Run race detector\ngo test ./pkg/workloadmanager/... -race\n\n# Run benchmarks\ngo test ./pkg/workloadmanager/... -bench=. -benchmem\n```\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- testify (assert, require)\n- k8s.io/client-go (fake clients)\n- k8s.io/apimachinery (runtime, schema)\n- net/http/httptest\n\n---\n\n## Notes\n\n- All tests should use table-driven tests where appropriate\n- Mock implementations should be centralized (mockLogger pattern)\n- Integration tests should use fake K8s clients, not real clusters\n- Race conditions should be explicitly tested for concurrent operations\n- Test naming convention: Test<Struct>_<Method>_<Scenario>"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchma